May 24, 2014 RT give link to the video with Italian journalist and his russian-italian translator (girl) when Ukrainian military offensive near Sloviansk.  This video was shot shortly before they died.


After that, this video has been deleted from Youtube channel of the Abkhaz news agency ANNA News. And the agency channel was completely removed with no explanation. Maybe with pressure of the USA government.

